blaming you for the tech issues yet.

574
00:36:54,230 --> 00:36:56,078
Lin Jia Dong, the moment your aunt went down

575
00:36:56,078 --> 00:36:58,180
and you rushed over to pledge loyalty to us,

576
00:36:58,180 --> 00:37:00,633
I should've known you were just a fence-sitter.

577
00:37:00,633 --> 00:37:02,260
Let me save you the trouble.

578
00:37:02,260 --> 00:37:04,940
We're leaving with Lin right now.

579
00:37:08,110 --> 00:37:10,700
Men will always be boys until the day they die.

580
00:37:10,700 --> 00:37:12,010
Thank you.

581
00:37:12,010 --> 00:37:15,210
- But...
- Mr. Lin needs you to stay.

582
00:37:16,400 --> 00:37:19,184
Xue Jiao, what the company's doing now

583
00:37:19,184 --> 00:37:21,230
is no different from B&amp;C back then.

584
00:37:21,230 --> 00:37:22,900
If you want to stay, just stay.

585
00:37:22,900 --> 00:37:25,150
But I'm leaving.

586
00:37:25,150 --> 00:37:27,260
But even so, you should leave
with all the facts clear.

587
00:37:27,260 --> 00:37:30,090
What matters most now
is finding out what caused the accident.

588
00:37:30,090 --> 00:37:31,780
Don't act on impulse.

589
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:35,440
Lin, our accident investigation
team lost all access.

590
00:37:35,440 --> 00:37:36,670
